title: Ebro In The Morning - Drake & Ye Beef Squashed? + You Don't Know White Sh*t Wednesday
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 11/17.

Ebro and the crew discuss Ye and Drake squashing their beef, the Flashing Lights reports shine light on the days biggest news(8, 30, and 1:09), and Rosenberg quizzes the crew on White Shit (39).
